data.description: Welcome to this well maintained 1970s home, offering peace of mind with its newer HVAC systems (2021), recently sealed air ducts (2021), new water heater (2023), a newer roof (2018), and stucco being done in 2018. The upper level features a cozy kitchen with granite countertops, ideal for home cooking. Step outside to a spacious deck for entertaining and a large backyard with convenient access to the lower level. With plenty of bedrooms and a bathroom on both levels.
